01:27:45,760 --> 01:27:47,728
Uh, no...

1555
01:27:47,762 --> 01:27:49,252
Your hand is up.

1556
01:27:52,834 --> 01:27:55,860
Oh, it, it's, uh, not a question,

1557
01:27:55,903 --> 01:27:58,167
