how wonderful they are.

1583
01:29:41,275 --> 01:29:43,300
You have a beautiful family.

1584
01:29:45,146 --> 01:29:47,273
Don't let this
come between you.

1585
01:29:50,318 --> 01:29:52,616
This was my fault.

1586
01:29:52,653 --> 01:29:54,484
Margaret...

1587
01:29:54,522 --> 01:29:56,422
Andrew, this was a business deal,

1588
01:29:56,457 --> 01:30:00,484
