but now the deal is off.

1589
01:30:01,762 --> 01:30:03,059
I'm sorry.

1590
01:30:04,966 --> 01:30:06,194
And, you, meet me at the dock.

1591
01:30:06,234 --> 01:30:08,031
You're giving me a ride to the airport.

1592
01:30:24,852 --> 01:30:27,343
- What were you thinking?
- I don't, I don't know.

1593
01:30:27,388 --> 01:30:28,980
