01:31:16,203 --> 01:31:17,465
<i>I'd lose you as an assistant</i>

1600
01:31:17,505 --> 01:31:19,735
<i>but... you have an extraordinary eye,</i>

1601
01:31:19,774 --> 01:31:22,800
<i>and I'll make sure we
buy this before I leave.</i>

1602
01:31:22,843 --> 01:31:26,973
<i>Have an amazing life.
You deserve it. Margaret.</i>

1603
01:31:29,216 --> 01:31:32,447
Well, that was, uh... crazy.

1604
01:31:33,854 --> 01:31:36,288
You know, people are gonna be
talking about this forever.

1605
01:31:38,192 --> 01:31:39,819
Yeah. Yeah.

1606
01:31:41,529 --> 01:31:42,655
Are you OK?

1607
01:31:43,898 --> 01:31:46,765
Yeah. No. Uh...

1608
01:31:48,936 --> 01:31:52,804
I just feel... You know
what the problem is?

1609
01:31:52,840 --> 01:31:56,037
The problem is that this woman...

1610
01:31:56,077 --> 01:31:59,604
