1616
01:32:12,126 --> 01:32:17,223
Three years. Three years
I work with this... this terrorist.

1617
01:32:17,264 --> 01:32:18,856
Never once has she had
a nice thing to say,

1618
01:32:18,899 --> 01:32:20,764
and then she goes ahead
and she writes this crap!

1619
01:32:20,801 --> 01:32:22,564
- Andrew.
- But none of that matters

1620
01:32:22,603 --> 01:32:23,831
because we had a deal!

1621
01:32:23,871 --> 01:32:28,069
- Andrew.
- Sorry. I'm sorry. I just...

1622
01:32:28,109 --> 01:32:29,303
She just makes me a little crazy.

1623
01:32:29,343 --> 01:32:32,779
Yeah. I can see that.

1624
01:32:32,813 --> 01:32:36,874
So you're just gonna let her go?

1625
01:32:50,164 --> 01:32:52,132
So, what now?

1626
01:32:52,166 --> 01:32:55,135
Well... now that
you're leaving voluntarily,

1627
01:32:55,169 --> 01:32:57,865
