1628
01:32:57,905 --> 01:33:00,669
Once we land in New York,
you have 24 hours

1629
01:33:00,708 --> 01:33:03,734
to head back to Canada.

1630
01:33:11,118 --> 01:33:13,450
- Andrew, what's happening?
- I got to talk to her.

1631
01:33:13,487 --> 01:33:14,715
