01:36:58,279 --> 01:36:59,746
That he loves her.

1691
01:36:59,780 --> 01:37:02,613
So she could tell him
that she loves him, too.

1692
01:37:02,650 --> 01:37:03,810
OK, but how does he...

1693
01:37:03,851 --> 01:37:05,216
